<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/general.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/game.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
        <div class="container mt-5 vh-75">
            <div class="card mb-3">
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="d-flex card-img-container">
                        <img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1086940/header.jpg?t=1725654125"
                            class="rounded-start card-picture" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-50">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="card-title">Baldurs Gate</h2>
                            <p class="card-text">Fecha de lanzamiento: 3 Oct 2024</p>
                            <h5>Descripcion:</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Reúne a tu grupo y vuelve a los Reinos Olvidados en un relato de
                                compañerismo y traición,
                                sacrificio y supervivencia, además de la atracción de un poder absoluto.</p>
                            <div class="container border-top mt-5 px-0 d-flex">
                                <div class="container mt-3">
                                    <h5>Generalmente favorable</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Basado en 15 criticas</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="container w-25 d-flex my-3">
                                    <div class="bg-success align-content-center text-center w-100 rounded">
                                        <h2 class="p-2">100</h2>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="container d-flex mt-5 w-100">
                                <button class="btn btn-success w-100" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                                    data-bs-target="#reviewModal">Agregar reseña</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <h3 class="border-bottom">Reseñas</h3>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card mb-3 mt-3 border" style="max-width: 540px;">
                        <div class="row g-0">
                            <div class="card-body review-card-header">
                                <div class="user-score">5</div>
                                <h4 class="username ms-4">pospos56</h4>
                                <p class="date text-end col "><small>OCT 6, 2024</small></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body review-card-content">
                                <p>the game was not bad but the animation went the character talk the mouth animation is
                                    not in accordance and the animation too but the gameplay its still okay</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card mb-3 mt-3 bg-dark" style="max-width: 540px;">
                        <div class="row g-0">
                            <div class="card-body review-card-header">
                                <div class="user-score text-light">5</div>
                                <h4 class="username ms-4 text-light">pospos56</h4>
                                <p class="date text-end col text-light"><small>OCT 6, 2024</small></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body review-card-content text-light">
                                <p>the game was not bad but the animation went the character talk the mouth animation is
                                    not in accordance and the animation too but the gameplay its still okay</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card mb-3 mt-3 bg-dark" style="max-width: 540px;">
                        <div class="row g-0">
                            <div class="card-body review-card-header">
                                <div class="user-score text-light">5</div>
                                <h4 class="username ms-4 text-light">pospos56</h4>
                                <p class="date text-end col text-light"><small>OCT 6, 2024</small></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body review-card-content text-light">
                                <p>the game was not bad but the animation went the character talk the mouth animation is
                                    not in accordance and the animation too but the gameplay its still okay</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card mb-3 mt-3 bg-dark" style="max-width: 540px;">
                        <div class="row g-0">
                            <div class="card-body review-card-header">
                                <div class="user-score text-light">5</div>
                                <h4 class="username ms-4 text-light">pospos56</h4>
                                <p class="date text-end col text-light"><small>OCT 6, 2024</small></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body review-card-content text-light">
                                <p>the game was not bad but the animation went the character talk the mouth animation is
                                    not in accordance and the animation too but the gameplay its still okay</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="modal fade" id="reviewModal" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false" tabindex="-1"
            aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header border-0">
                        <h3 class="modal-title" id="staticBackdropLabel">Agregar mi reseña</h3>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <div class="container d-flex pb-3 border-bottom">
                            <img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1086940/header.jpg?t=1725654125"
                                class="modal-img" alt="">
                            <h4 class="card-title ms-4">Baldurs Gate</h4>
                        </div>
                        <div class="container d-flex rating-container p-0 my-3">
                            <div class="current-rating me-3">6</div>
                            <div class="rating-number bad mx-1">1</div>
                            <div class="rating-number bad mx-1">2</div>
                            <div class="rating-number bad mx-1">3</div>
                            <div class="rating-number decent mx-1">4</div>
                            <div class="rating-number decent mx-1">5</div>
                            <div class="rating-number decent mx-1">6</div>
                            <div class="rating-number decent mx-1">7</div>
                            <div class="rating-number good mx-1">8</div>
                            <div class="rating-number good mx-1">9</div>
                            <div class="rating-number good mx-1">10</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="container mt-3 border-top">
                            <label for="reviewComment" class="form-label">Escribi tu reseña.</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="reviewComment" rows="3"></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex border-0">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary m-3 w-50"
                            data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancelar</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary m-3 w-50">Publicar</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
</body>

</html>